body: Good Ol' wincest, can't say much for it other then it's a sweet story, the art style is quite good not the best but gets the job done the psychological element which makes this even better is superb as well, I liked the contrast of the boy being mad at his mother but not batshit insane like many other hentai's portray these types of scenes, the blowjob, and sex scenes were good as well. all in all, I rate this a 7.5/10
